&lt;p&gt;BeyondTrust is a place where you can bring your purpose to life through the work that you do, creating a safer world through our cybersecurity SaaS portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our culture of flexibility, trust, and continual learning means you will be recognized for your growth, and for the impact you make on our success. You will be surrounded by people who challenge, support, and inspire you to be the best version of yourself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;The Role&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Senior Account Executive to join our LATAM team, selling in Monterrey, Mexico. It will be responsible for accounts across the North region of Mexico, especially the Monterrey area, and as such, the preferred location for the candidates is the Monterrey area. This is a hunter role with some upselling opportunities in existing accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct and coordinate activities regarding the sale of company products/solutions by contacting prospects and leads to generate interest and qualify demand.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to cross-sell and upsell within the existing customer base.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cultivate strong relationships with key decision-makers and influencers throughout sales efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as advisor to clients, maintaining a knowledge base of technical and industry information as well as reporting on industry fluctuations and market conditions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend corporate trade shows and events, as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schedule and conduct high-level demonstrations and detailed presentations to prospects, customers, and partners; lead RFPs and communicate with internal stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate sales pipeline activity and records in Salesforce, and analyze sales statistics gathered by staff to determine sales potential and inventory requirements and monitor customer preferences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;What You’ll Bring&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in business, Marketing, or a related field preferred or relevant experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10 years of full-time work experience in a customer-facing sales role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;IT Knowledge – Microsoft tools knowledge and the ability to use as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tenacity, independence, and ambition are required to make this role your own.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven record of overachieving quota and results in a high-growth company environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Nice To Have&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Undertaken relevant sales training.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of security, PAM, identity management or related software a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;What Will Make You Successful&lt;br&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conviction and Commitment.&amp;nbsp;You have an unshakable belief that BeyondTrust’s products will improve the world – one person at a time. Once you get it, you go all the way.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A True Team Player. You’re the best at what you do, and you know how to work with your teammates to get their best.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Energy and Enthusiasm. You believe in what we’re doing and won’t stop at anything to deliver to your goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent Communication. You know what to say and more importantly, how to say it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ownership&amp;nbsp;– You take ownership of your results and often look for ways to improve; you see challenges as opportunities instead of obstacles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Go-Getter. Willing to go the extra mile with a strong work ethic; self-directed and resourceful.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Better Together&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Diversity. Inclusion. They’re more than just words for us. They are the guiding values of how we build our teams, cultivate leaders, and create a culture where people feel connected.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We take care of our employees so they can take care of our customers. Customers who&amp;nbsp;come from all walks of life just like us. We hire incredible people from diverse backgrounds because when we are different together, we are stronger together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;About Us&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BeyondTrust is the global identity security leader protecting Paths to Privilege™. Our identity-centric approach goes beyond securing privileges and access, empowering organizations with the most effective solution to manage the entire identity attack surface and neutralize threats, whether from external attacks or insiders.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;BeyondTrust is leading the charge in transforming identity security to prevent breaches and limit the blast radius of attacks, while creating a superior customer experience and operational efficiencies. We are trusted by 20,000 customers, including 75 of the Fortune 100, and our global ecosystem of partners.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Learn more at &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.beyondtrust.com/&quot;&gt;www.beyondtrust.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
